# Swim Intervals [Pool Swimming] (2026-03-10 06:30-07:30)
@ location: 50m Olympic Pool
@ equipment: pull buoy, paddles

- Swim 400m @Z1
  > Easy freestyle warmup, focus on catch.
- 4x:
  - Swim 100m @Z4
  - Recover 50m @Z1
- 2x:
  - Swim 200m @Z3
  - Recover 100m @Z1
- Swim 200m @Z1

> Total: 2000m. Splits were consistent on the 100s — 1:28-1:30 per 100m.
